{"tid":1159082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"水原希子遠赴法國爆乳參加康城影展 搭 Uber 被問「拍色情片嗎」聽完超生氣","createTime":"2019-05-17T11:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T20:30:24.000Z","uid":9573,"like":8,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c91ec9b28ae1a096181ef291c1cd9350d48711d8","tid":1159082,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"第72屆坎城影展正在如火如荼進行中，美韓混血女模水原希子日前盛裝亮相法國參加坎城影展，不過水原希子卻在網上發文抱怨，在巴黎被Uber司機問「是拍色情片嗎？」讓水原希子氣炸！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-05-17/900/20190517003090.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-05-17%2F900%2F20190517003090.jpg&h=8333c591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水原希子日前身穿平口低胸銀綠色禮服亮相坎城影展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/05/10/1/4725080.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F1%2F4725080.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=492522eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本女星水原希子與大陸女星王麗坤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3278/e3278355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3278%2Fe3278355.jpg&h=06be374f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水原希子大方曬酥胸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180511/large/11ee2p5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180511%2Flarge%2F11ee2p5a.jpg&h=59c71553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水原希子風騷轉身擺動長裙，在紅地毯大送飛吻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N3wzuLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN3wzuLA.jpg&h=e48189f8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n很想被她挨著睡覺的朱千雪。<br />\n<br />\n水原希子日前以一襲平口低胸銀綠色禮服亮相坎城影展，大方曬酥胸，她也陸續在IG曬美照，不過水原希子近日卻在Twitter不吐不快，她在巴黎搭Uber時，被司機問是什麼職業，她回答是女演員，沒想到對方竟問她「是拍色情片嗎？」讓水原希子聽完超生氣，轟司機失禮且不尊重女性。"},{"pid":"a6d1719798c7077f97052303935f6de8fd08b987","tid":1159082,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"重口味"},{"pid":"9aa01609c68b756671ffeca6c93fab026a9a9396","tid":1159082,"uid":81308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"係  fake taxi"},{"pid":"233126db739f6007cd5d279392b05af187ea930f","tid":1159082,"uid":58871,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"為左千雪入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3806109b3de60bcd1fd556e74507e90fc417b6","tid":1159082,"uid":140335,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"爆乳?<br />\n係咪爆到移為平地嘅乳?"},{"pid":"77b3a5b85af415689c2afe10a4ac311f89aafb2b","tid":1159082,"uid":199417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aa01609c68b756671ffeca6c93fab026a9a9396","tid":1159082,"uid":81308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"係  fake taxi"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"fake uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e4c9e6b30eb8489f4ebe31e87a8ba29d3d5781","tid":1159082,"uid":37757,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/e/eb/12187791_188705991467213_5301158756329322348_n.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20151026141843&amp;format=original\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fe%2Feb%2F12187791_188705991467213_5301158756329322348_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20151026141843%26format%3Doriginal&h=7bcba4e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e6ac875657463ba249da0cf2e28813ce3b8419a","